00:17:38,044 --> 00:17:40,846
and the game does something that catches them by surprise

261
00:17:41,226 --> 00:17:45,307
in a good way so that they maybe burst out laughing in surprise.

262
00:17:45,327 --> 00:17:48,769
Like, whoa, the game did this kind of a thing? What?

263
00:17:48,989 --> 00:17:49,409
That kind of...

