00:19:01,323 --> 00:19:06,406
system. This actually just to pause for a moment and talk about the game being

277
00:19:06,466 --> 00:19:11,410
played here. So it's actually a very good kind of non-tutorial moment that I

278
00:19:11,450 --> 00:19:16,073
should have maybe tutorialized better which is that there are these

279
00:19:16,549 --> 00:19:18,009
two new words, open and shut.

280
00:19:18,770 --> 00:19:21,710
