00:31:18,668 --> 00:31:22,169
A robot is kind of clinical, often, not always,

429
00:31:22,209 --> 00:31:23,869
but often kind of boring.

430
00:31:24,249 --> 00:31:27,170
It's a very easy, this kind of non-personal,

